@DATABASE "Way Of The Exploding Fist II"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - W - Way Of The Exploding Fist II"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - W
                   ====================================

                       Way Of The Exploding Fist II
                       ============================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(27061,0)"}          27061,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(27233,255)"}          27233,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         Rastan.
@endnode
